{"tid":1787653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃色經濟圈嘅突破口！","createTime":"2019-12-18T05:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T20:00:42.000Z","uid":167548,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c36630f9ca1eb45b1c5f9872d999157c28970229","tid":1787653,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">引外資 引外資 引外資</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n取代在港中資成為香港嘅外資代言人？<br />\n<br />\n狗官咁驚黃圈, 是因為鬼佬多左嗰選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個誠實可靠, 居合約精神嘅partner<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰問題是會唔會有支那人扮黃搞臭香港人嘅朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe93c13915f09174f7fcddc3e163949a57a1de97","tid":1787653,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"不過諗深入一層, 中美貿易戰下外國條水都沒曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5389673abcb1f03fe72597fae38b78ab20f5741","tid":1787653,"uid":76922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈一定會放大<br />\n要搵人整一個似openrice咁嘅app<br />\n有齊間店嘅原因 information 餐牌 地點 電話<br />\n咁先會咁快捷方便 <br />\n而且你係時候要向各國登報<br />\n交代至目前為止幾多手足傷/亡/失蹤/警曱暴力惡行<br />\n要用數字交代！要有good design! <br />\n同時宣傳 要求各國共同反共同抗議 到當地各蝗國大事館示威 <br />\n而本地要轉換形式 <br />\n針對三權分立制度攻擊<br />\n遊行，集會，罷工，抗暴一定要有死線交代<br />\n否則會停滯不前<br />\n要香港人行多步 <br />\n一齊升級<br />\n罷藍店 要有確實行動！"},{"pid":"50ceebb414c5b36d521c56998ace724c04ce9521","tid":1787653,"uid":323983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco